com.adobe.aemforms.fm.model

Class FormsetOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.aemforms.fm.model.FormsetOptions

  • public class FormsetOptions
extends Object
    FormsetOptions represents the Form Set Configurable properties that will be honored while creating Form Set through FormGenerationService.

      • setRenderProfile

        public void setRenderProfile(String renderProfile)
        sets profile REST endpoint that contains associated Profile Renderer. Profile Renderer are JSP pages responsible for generating HTML representation of the Form Set by calling the Forms OSGi service. Default profile is set to "/content/forms/formsets/profiles/default"
        Parameters:
        renderProfile - String representing render profile.

      • setFormsetItemList

        public void setFormsetItemList(List<FormsetItem> formsetItemList)
        sets the List of FormsetOtem in this Form Set. FormsetItem contains the details of a Form in this Form Set. This is mandatory field to specify. If null or empty, Form Set creation will FAIL.
        Parameters:
        formsetItemList - representing List Forms in this Form Set.

        Parameters:

        public void setName(String name)
        Sets the name of the Form Set. If characters other than alphabets, numbers, hyphens and underscores are specified, will be replaced by hyphens. This is mandatory field to specify. If null or empty, Form Set creation will FAIL.
        Parameters:
